{"tid":683161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：街頭力抗五警　壽司賊成口血","createTime":"2018-05-29T12:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T15:30:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"324559556a8a65e78e4865dbc0b9adcb6d0a97b5","tid":683161,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:48:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180529/20404643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F20404643&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96b%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3876074e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F20404643&h=9fab019a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180529/20404643</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月29日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：街頭力抗五警　壽司賊成口血<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180529/large/a1304a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180529%2Flarge%2Fa1304a.gif&h=49e9765a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■偷壽司賊被阿Sir擒住，壽司跌滿一地。讀者陳先生提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣一間超市喺星期六俾人偷嘢，有個中年男人偷咗幾盒壽司準備慢慢嘆，點知原來阿Sir老早贒到佢，等到小偷行出超市門口，便衣警員就人贓並獲，當場將佢㩒低拘捕。不過對方激烈反抗，搞到頭同口都撞到流晒血，有圍觀途人仲以為疑犯咬脷自殺，最後男子俾阿Sir鎖上手銬，送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n間超市位於記利佐治街，人流都好旺，咁啱阿Sir喺附近一帶進行反盜竊巡邏，小偷當場斷正啦。事發喺星期六傍晚，讀者陳先生見到一個中年男子攞住幾盒壽司走出超市，突然有兩位便衣阿Sir衝出嚟將佢拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n個男人當時爆晒粗唔肯就範，極力掙扎，其後兩、三個阿Sir增援，四、五個阿Sir終於合力將個男人制服喺地上，嗰幾盒壽司就跌到通地都係。警方證實拉咗個32歲姓余男子，佢涉嫌店舖盜竊，喺超市偷咗300蚊食物。<br />\n<br />\n警方又承認疑犯一度情緒激動，頭同口受傷，事後送去律敦治醫院治理。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：住戶：阿Sir金睛火眼做到嘢<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：漁署封深灣護龜　遭網民秒殺"},{"pid":"a042f9a8344d25c2900d8765758969e292f51396","tid":683161,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:50:40.000Z","msg":"壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66aba7c715085f37133a702bb841f0edf0244c37","tid":683161,"uid":69994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:10:14.000Z","msg":"英勇五虎成功起回大批贓物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180529/large/a1304a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180529%2Flarge%2Fa1304a.gif&h=0583d809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.handedict.de/jt/zi/images/hanzi/song/medium/%E8%B4%92_song.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.handedict.de%2Fjt%2Fzi%2Fimages%2Fhanzi%2Fsong%2Fmedium%2F%25E8%25B4%2592_song.png&h=65c760cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8c9f8cde3f599bc2bc065c1e0f9c306d456aabb","tid":683161,"uid":48631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/9-09-2016/R6Lzxn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F9-09-2016%2FR6Lzxn.gif&h=cdaa041c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"978f72d2f170e7908ca41a087cd8dec6cbdd4cac","tid":683161,"uid":38216,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"啲廢中買盒壽司都冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677a0a31c968f8b416f7514d74e2384b6105b31a","tid":683161,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:25:43.000Z","msg":"死崇日狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9268dca26dd50d52fbe8771aa2a3aa7a5f1f2004","tid":683161,"uid":131157,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:26:34.000Z","msg":"死黑警打到人成口血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji